    <item>
      <title>司法部最高官方命令检察官向纽约市市长埃里克·亚当斯（Eric Adams）提出指控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-02-10/urgent-top-justice-department-official-orders-prosecutors-to-drop-charges-against-new-york-mayor-eric-adams</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约（AP）＆Mdash;司法部周一命令联邦检察官对纽约市市长埃里克·亚当斯（Eric Adams）撤销腐败指控，这与长期的检察官规范相去甚远，该案件正在干预市长对非法移民和暴力犯罪的侵犯的能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-02-10/urgent-top-justice-department-official-orders-prosecutors-to-drop-charges-against-new-york-mayor-eric-adams</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Feb 2025 23:55:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚为关键矿物质和氢化税收减免</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/australia-to-enact-tax-breaks-for-critical-minerals-and-hydrogen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚将为预计将于周二通过议会的立法下生产可再生氢或处理关键矿产的公司提供税收激励措施，这是中左派政府的最新举动，以促进国内绿色工业并加强供应链。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/australia-to-enact-tax-breaks-for-critical-minerals-and-hydrogen</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Feb 2025 22:50:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普对钢铁，随着贸易战的增长，铝征收25％的关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/trump-sets-25-tariffs-on-steel-aluminum-heightening-trade-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统下令对钢铁和铝业进口征收25％的关税，并升级了他为保护政治重要行业的努力，税收击中了该国一些最接近的盟友。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/trump-sets-25-tariffs-on-steel-aluminum-heightening-trade-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Feb 2025 22:39:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚说，特朗普同意考虑对关税的豁免</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/albanese-says-trump-will-consider-australia-tariff-exemption</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统已同意考虑与总理安东尼·阿尔巴尼斯（Anthony Albanese）打来电话后，即使他最初表示不例外，澳大利亚在与总理安东尼·阿尔巴尼斯（Anthony Albanese）打了电话后，对澳大利亚的钢铁和铝业关税进行了豁免。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/albanese-says-trump-will-consider-australia-tariff-exemption</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Feb 2025 22:16:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔（Powell</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/powell-heads-for-hyper-charged-hearings-overshadowed-by-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔（Jerome Powell）本周在国会山（Capitol Hill）面临着一场艰难的听证会，民主党人和共和党人都可能会根据总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的政策，从银行法规到多样性，公平和包容性工作的回滚，这些政策已经吞没了中央中央的努力银行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/powell-heads-for-hyper-charged-hearings-overshadowed-by-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Feb 2025 17:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普简化了禁止海外贿赂的法律执行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/trump-to-loosen-enforcement-of-us-law-banning-overseas-bribes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统签署了一项行政命令，撤销了一项法律的执行，该法律禁止美国公司贿赂外国官员，并认为限制使美国公司处于不利地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/trump-to-loosen-enforcement-of-us-law-banning-overseas-bribes</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Feb 2025 17:29:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普告诉以色列如果人质未返回，取消停火</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/trump-says-palestinians-won-t-have-right-of-return-in-gaza-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统说，如果本周末没有返回人质，以色列应取消与哈马斯的停火协议，最新信号表明脆弱的六周休战可能处于失败的边缘。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/trump-says-palestinians-won-t-have-right-of-return-in-gaza-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Feb 2025 16:56:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
